<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8141804>
    dc:description "FIGURE 16. A comparison of allied species. A–B. Thrixspermum simile. C–D. T. lampongense. E–F. T. centipeda. Photographed by Wattana Tanming (A–B. Cultivation, QSBG), Nopparut Toolmal (C–D. Cultivation, QSBG) & Pilchar Ngai (E–F, Cultivation, Hong Kong). Illustration assembled by Yongyuth Rattanasootr." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8141804/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8141824>
    dc:description "FIGURE 24. A comparison of allied species. A–B. Thrixspermum polystictum. C–D. T. latisaccatum. E–F. Thrixspermum simile. Photographed by Wattana Tanming (A–F. Cultivation, QSBG). Illustration assembled by Yongyuth Rattanasootr." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8141824/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8141828>
    dc:description "FIGURE 27. Distribution map of Thrixspermum simile and T. polystictum in Thailand and Cambodia. It could represent a different taxon." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8141828/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8141812>
    dc:description "FIGURE 19. Thrixspermum flammeum. A–B. Plant habit. C. Inflorescences with flowers. D–E. Flower (ventral view). F. Flower (lateral view). Photographed by André Schuiteman (A. In situ, Champasak, Laos), Chaiwat Tunkpradit (B. In situ, Thailand), Wattana Tanming (C–E. Cultivation, QSBG) & Nopparut Toolmal (F. Cultivation, QSBG). Illustration assembled by Yongyuth Rattanasootr." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8141812/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

